1:11:32.873 --> 1:11:34.333
You really don't remember.

1:11:44.677 --> 1:11:46.136
You feeling okay, chief?

1:12:06.407 --> 1:12:08.826
<i>That's what the control,
the regimen, the journal,</i>

1:12:08.909 --> 1:12:10.744
<i>my perfectly constructed loop,</i>

1:12:11.036 --> 1:12:12.746
<i>what this whole
thing's been about.</i>

1:12:28.220 --> 1:12:31.015
<i>Last night till this morning,
while I was sleeping,</i>

1:12:31.265 --> 1:12:32.599
<i>I can't account for it,</i>

1:12:32.683 --> 1:12:35.019
<i>a gap in my consciousness,
and somehow he...</i>

1:12:35.102 --> 1:12:37.354
What do they see
when they see you coming?

1:12:39.940 --> 1:12:41.525
<i>And this is why I'm different.</i>

1:12:42.443 --> 1:12:44.611
<i>Sometimes my mask takes over.</i>

1:12:44.778 --> 1:12:46.405
Why did you talk to him?

1:12:49.074 --> 1:12:50.743
Because I'm gonna
make you realize.

1:12:51.744 --> 1:12:52.870
What?

1:12:57.541 --> 1:12:59.209
What will you make me realize?

1:13:06.967 --> 1:13:08.594
That they see me.

1:14:29.716 --> 1:14:30.801
What's so funny?

1:14:30.884 --> 1:14:33.887
We started a movement.
We were meant to lead it.

1:14:33.971 --> 1:14:35.722
Now, get back
on a terminal now.

1:14:35.806 --> 1:14:38.183
Give me what I want
or keep shooting me.

1:14:43.188 --> 1:14:48.318
Tell me where Tyrell is,
or shoot me again

1:14:51.405 --> 1:14:53.532
'cause the only one
it's gonna drive mad is you...

1:14:55.159 --> 1:14:56.326
Not me.

1:15:31.945 --> 1:15:33.447
I'm late for my church group.

1:15:35.282 --> 1:15:36.450
Peace.

1:15:43.373 --> 1:15:45.209
<i>...this time targeting
the Bank of E network</i>

1:15:45.292 --> 1:15:47.586
<i>in an elaborate
ransomware attack.</i>

1:15:47.961 --> 1:15:50.464
<i>The malicious malware targeted
the bank's computer servers</i>

1:15:50.547 --> 1:15:52.799
<i>and spread to
multiple branches
